“The films will premiere where?!” 

A look back at the shock and excitement as @Tribeca, @QueenLatifah and Marc Pritchard kicked off the Year 3 #QueenCollective mentorship program.

The films premiere this Thursday at the 2021 #TribecaFilmFestival.
